%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22600%20People%20Shot%20Dead%20%26quot%3BWithin%20Hours%26quot%3B%20By%20Al-Qaeda%20In%20This%20African%20Country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAbout%20600%20people%20were%20killed%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20by%20members%20affiliated%20with%20Al-Qaeda%20in%20an%20August%20attack%20on%20the%20town%20of%20Barsalogho%20in%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20a%20report%20claimed%20on%20Friday.%20The%20residents%20of%20Barsalogho%20were%20shot%20dead%20on%20August%2024%20as%20they%20dug%20protective%20trenches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%2C%20in%20which%20most%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20women%20and%20children%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F170-people-executed-in-attacks-on-3-villages-in-burkina-faso-report-5167872%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20West%20African%20country's%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20a%20jihadist%20insurgency%20waged%20by%20rebels%20affiliated%20with%20Al-Qaeda%20and%20the%20Islamic%20State%20group%20that%20spilled%20over%20from%20neighbouring%20Mali%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20Jama'at%20Nusrat%20al-Islam%20wal-Muslimin%20(JNIM)%2C%20an%20Al-Qaeda%20affiliate%20based%20in%20Mali%20and%20active%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrowns-not-greens-how-an-arid-africa-country-is-reimagining-golf-courses-3876165%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurkina%20Faso%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shot%20down%20villagers%20as%20they%20swept%20into%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Barsalogho%20on%20bikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20United%20Nations%20estimated%20a%20death%20count%20of%20around%20200%2C%20JNIM%20said%20it%20had%20killed%20nearly%20300%20%26quot%3Bfighters%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F04%2Fafrica%2Fburkina-faso-massacre-600-dead-french-intel-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%