0races%20of%20the%20century%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20Ben%20and%20Felicia%20Horowitz's%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2016%2C%20just%20days%20before%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20race%2C%20Horowitz%20and%20his%20close%20business%20partner%20Marc%20Andreessen%20said%20in%20their%20podcast%20that%20Trump%20would%20better%20support%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-little-tech-us-global-leadership-marc-andreessen-ben-horowitz-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemerging%20technology%20companies%20and%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20our%20business%2C%20the%20future%20of%20technology%2C%20new%20technology%2C%20and%20the%20future%20of%20America%20is%20literally%20at%20stake%2C%26quot%3B%20Horowitz%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BSo%20here%20we%20are.%20For%20little%20tech%2C%20we%20think%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20actually%20the%20right%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Horowitz%20wrote%20in%20the%20email%20to%20A16z%20employees%20that%20he'll%20be%20donating%20to%20entities%20supporting%20the%20Harris-Walz%20campaign%2C%20the%20venture%20capitalist%20noted%20that%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20hear%20what%20the%20campaign's%20tech%20policies%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20I%20have%20had%20several%20conversations%20with%20Vice%20President%20Harris%20and%20her%20team%20on%20their%20likely%20tech%20policies%20and%20am%20encouraged%20by%20my%20belief%20in%20her%2C%20they%20have%20not%20yet%20stated%20what%20their%20tech%20policy%20will%20be%2C%20so%20the%20firm%20will%20not%20be%20updating%20its%20position%20in%20that%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20email%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3Ea16zers%2C%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20wanted%20to%20give%20you%20an%20update%20on%20my%20political%20activity.%20As%20I%20mentioned%20before%2C%20Fel