ay%2C%20BJP%20Eyes%20Hat-Trick%2C%20Congress%20A%20Comeback%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20eyeing%20a%20hat-trick%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20hoping%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%20Haryana%20after%20a%20decade.%20The%20other%20key%20contestants%20are%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20and%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20(ASP).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP's%20campaign%20was%20spearheaded%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20addressed%20four%20rallies%2C%20where%20he%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20on%20several%20issues%20and%20said%20they%20kept%20every%20matter%20important%20for%20the%20country%20entangled%2C%20including%20the%20Ram%20temple%20issue.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20also%20addressed%20many%20public%20meetings%20where%20he%20said%20a%20%26quot%3BCongress%20storm%26quot%3B%20is%20on%20its%20way%20in%20Haryana%20and%20his%20party%20would%20form%20the%20government%2C%20which%20will%20be%20one%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20farmers%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bmohabbat%20ki%20dukan%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20opened%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20left%20the%20Bhiwani%20assembly%20seat%20for%20its%20INDIA%20bloc%20partner%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20or%20CPI(M)%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20contesting%20the%20Sirsa%20seat%2C%20from%20where%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%20chief%20Gopal%20Kanda%20is%20seeking%20re-election.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMost%20seats%20are%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20direct%20fight%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%20Prominent%20among%20them%20are%20Chief%20Minister%20Saini%20(Ladwa)%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Hooda%20(Garhi%20Sampla-Kiloi)%2C%20INLD's%20Abhay%20Singh%20Chautala%20(Ellenabad)%2C%20JJP's%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20(Uch