0fair%20and%20peaceful%20conduct%20of%20elections.%20Over%2030%2C000%20police%20personnel%20and%20225%20paramilitary%20companies%20have%20been%20deployed.%20Of%20the%20total%20voters%2C%201.07%20crore%20are%20men%2C%2095%20lakh%20are%20women%2C%20and%20467%20are%20transgenders.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20October%208.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20are%208%2C821%20voters%20aged%20over%20100%2C%20including%203%2C283%20men%20and%205%2C538%20women.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20service%20voters%20is%201.09%20lakh.%20Notably%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20recorded%20in%202019%20assembly%20polls%20was%20around%2068%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728089880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4smjkob_voting-generic-ani_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-voting-2024-haryana-votes-today-bjp-eyes-hat-trick-congress-a-comeback-10-points-6718303%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20fortunes%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20besides%20JJP's%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20and%20over%201%2C000%20other%20candidates%20will%20be%20decided%20today%2C%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20vote%20for%2090%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Hit%20Iran's%20nuclear%20...'%3A%20Trump%20on%20how%20Israel%20should%20respond%20to%20missile%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728087017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113953014%2Cimgsize-913664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-israel-should-hit-irans-nuclear-first-days-after-biden-urges-restraint%2Farti