%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20press%20release%2C%20Meta%20called%20Movie%20Gen%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20advanced%20and%20immersive%20storytelling%20suite%20of%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20video%20generation%2C%20audio%20generation%2C%20personalized%20video%20generation%2C%20and%20video%20editing.%20The%20models%20were%20trained%20using%20publicly%20available%20data%20and%20licensed%20data%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20text%20prompt%2C%20Movie%20Gen%20can%20create%20videos%20up%20to%2016%20seconds%20long%20at%2016%20frames%20a%20second%20while%20reasoning%20%26quot%3Babout%20object%20motion%2C%20subject-object%20interactions%2C%20and%20camera%20motion.%26quot%3B%20Users%20can%20upload%20a%20picture%20of%20themselves%20to%20be%20incorporated%20into%20personalized%20videos%2C%20and%20Movie%20Gen%20can%20edit%20videos%20with%20text%20instructions%20from%20the%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta's%20example%20video%20shows%20an%20underwater%20perspective%20of%20a%20baby%20hippo%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-tiktok-makeup-trend-right-now-moo-deng-blush-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoo%20Deng%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reference%2C%20anyone%3F)%20happily%20swimming%20around%20in%20a%20serene%20aquatic%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20shows%20a%20koala%20on%20a%20surfboard%20and%20the%20accompanying%20prompt%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20fluffy%20koala%20bear%20surfs.%20It%20has%20a%20gray%20and%20white%20coat%20and%20a%20round%20nose.%20The%20surfboard%20is%20yellow.%20The%20koala%20bear%20is%20holding%20onto%20the%20surfboard%20with%20its%20paws.%20The%20koala%20bear's%20facial%20expression%20is%20focused.%20The%20sun%20is%20shining.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20audio%20generation%2C%20users%20can%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20and%20extend%20sound%20effects%2C%20background%20music%20or%20entire%20soundtracks%26quot%3B%20up%20to%2045%20seconds%20long%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said.%20An%20example%20clip%20of%20a%20