9%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultrawealthy%20travelers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20request%20celebrity-like%20treatment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20includes%20security%20and%20private%20hotel%20check-ins%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0even%20if%20they're%20not%20recognizably%20famous.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMillionaires%2C%20they're%20just%20like%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20see%20Instagram%20posts%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20surrounded%20by%20devoted%20followers%2C%20paparazzi%2C%20and%20motorcades%2C%20they%20also%20feel%20envious.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20when%20they%20travel%2C%20they%20can%20pay%20to%20replicate%20the%20feeling%20of%20fame%20and%20prestige.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Sienna%20India%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20ultra-luxury%20travel%20concierge%20service%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-billionaire-travelers-do-las-vegas-hotels-restaurants-shows-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESienna%20Charles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20most%20of%20her%20clients%20now%20request%20security%20and%20private%20hotel%20check-ins%2C%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20recognizable%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20calls%20this%20phenomenon%20the%20%26quot%3Bcelebritization%26quot%3B%20of%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20some%20of%20her%20customers%2C%20like%20singer%20Mariah%20Carey%20and%20former%20president%20George%20W.%20Bush's%20family%2C%20have%20obtained%20A-lister%20status.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20its%20100%20or%20so%20clients%20are%20finance%20executives%20with%20an%20average%20starting%20net%20worth%20of%20%24100%20million%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20pay%20the%20company's%20annual%20%2475%2C000%20to%20%24150%2C000%20membership%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20prefer%20to%20stay%20under%20the%20radar.%20But%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20the%20proliferation%20of%20Instagram%20%E2%80%94%20most%20have%20started%20wanting%20to%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20special%2C%20feel%20like%20a%20celebrity%2C%20and%20for%20people%20to%20know%20how%20much%20they're%20worth%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sienna%20Charles'%20clients%2C%20this%20means%20requesting%20security%2C%20hotel%20check-ins%20from%20the%20privacy%20of%20their%20car%20instead%20of%20at%20the%20front%20desk%2C%20and%20a%20motorcade%20of%20four%20to%20eight%20vehicles.%20They're%20not%20for%20an%20entourage%20%E2%80%94%20just%20to%20%26quot%3Barrive%20in%20style%2C%20emulating%20the%20glitz%20and%20glam%20they've%20seen%20in%20movies%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20want%20to%20be%20acknowledged%20from%20the%20first%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20India%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20achieving%20stardom%2C%20as%20Jeff%20Bezos%20has%20done%2C%20is%20their%20%26quot%3Blast%20frontier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Lauren%20S%C3%A1nchez%20on%20vanity%20fair%20red%20carpet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fee1c4a7031864927f3fbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIndia%20said%20Jeff%20Bezos%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20example%26quot%3B%20of%20Sienna%20Charles'%20clients'%20desire%20to%20transform%20from%20billionaire%20business%20owners%20into%20recognizable%20celebrities.%20%3Cp%3ERobert%20Smith%2FPatrick%20McMullan%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20the%20billionaire%20next%20door%2C%20and%20nobody%20knows%20who%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Sienna%20Charles'%20CEO%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20will%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%20for%20them%20the%20same%20way%20they%20would%20for%20a%20celebrity.%20But%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20separates%20them%20is%20what%20they%20don't%20have.%20Recognition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp