%20to%20see%20Govinda%20return%20to%20acting%20and%20dancing.%20He%20recalled%20being%20impressed%20by%20Govinda's%20dancing%20videos%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20casting%20in%20Ilzaam.%20Nihalani%20praised%20Govinda%20as%20a%20complete%20actor%2C%20expressing%20concern%20over%20recent%20controversy%2C%20but%20remains%20optimistic%20about%20his%20future%20contributions%20to%20cinema.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Bharti%20Dubey%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpahlaj-nihalani-reacts-to-controversy-surrounding-govindas-revolver-accident-i-dont-know-why-so-many-questions-are-being-asked-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F113948259.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUN%20Security%20Council%20Not%20Fixable%20In%20Current%20Format%26quot%3B%3A%20US%20Ex%20Envoy%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%20John%20Bolton%20today%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20a%20huge%20organisation%20and%20that%20many%20bodies%20of%20the%20global%20body%20are%20irrelevant.%20He%20said%20the%20UN's%20massive%20size%20is%20a%20part%20of%20its%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20specialised%20and%20technical%20agencies%20do%20good%20work%20when%20they%20stay%20out%20of%20politics.%20But%20the%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20are%20paralysed%20and%20therefore%20largely%20irrelevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bolton%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20sure%20if%20there%20is%20any%20way%20to%20bring%20meaningful%20reform.%20Many%20people%20have%20tried%20over%20the%20years%2C%20many%20suggestions%20have%20been%20given.%20It's%20very%20hard%20to%20see%20if%20any%20of%20them%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20bear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bolton's%20comments%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20world%20is%20beset%20by%20wars%2C%20humanitarian%20crises%20and%20other%20problems%2C%20bringing%20the%20focus%20back%20to%20whether%20the%20UN%20is%20becoming%20incapable%20of%20ensuring%20multilateral%20responses%20to%20solve%20serious%20global%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20the%20UN%20can%20address%20some%20of%20the%20problems%20-%20if%20it%20can%20-%20the%20former%20diplomat%20said%20it%20is%20important%20to%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20particular%20pieces%20of%20the%20UN%20because%20some%20pieces%20are%20clearly%20much%20much%20better%20than%20others%20when%20they%20do%20the%20work%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20are%20obscure%2C%20such%20as%20the%20World%20Intellectual%20Property%20Organisation%20which%20deals%20with%20a%20hugely%20important%20subject%20matter%20and%20so%20far%20we%20should%20keep%20our%20fingers%20crossed%20it%20has%20done%20good%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bolton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20not%20fixable%20at%20its%20current%20state%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Security%20Council%20I%20don't%20think%20is%20fixable%20in%20its%20current%20format%20where%20you%20have%20Russia%20and%20China%20in%20this%20increasingly%20close%20axis%20with%20China%20as%20the%20dominant%20partner%20determined%20to%20pursue%20their%20own%20interests.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20but%20not%20also%20dissimilar%20to%20the%20gridlock%20that%20was%20the%20cold%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bolton%20shared%20some%20suggestions%20as%20to%20what%20kinds%20of%20reforms%20may%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reforms%20that%20I%20have%20suggested%20are%20based%20on%20my%20very%20long%20experience%20in%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20and%20that%20is%20we%20need%20to%20change%20the%20funding%20system.%20I%20would%20eliminate%20the%20system%20of%20cess%20contribution%20where%20every%20nation%20pays%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20budget%20of%20different%20UN%20bodies%2C%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20entirely%20voluntary%20contributions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bolton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20radical%20theory%20that%20if%20something%20doesn't%20work%2C%20then%20you%20shouldn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20it.%20You%20should%20put%20your%20money%20in%20an%20institution%20that%20does%20work%20and%20I%20think%20that%20reform%20has%20very%20little%20chance%20of%20being%20adopted%20by%20the%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20I%20think%20is%20something%20that%20might%20actually%20wake%20the%20UN%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20been%20aspiring%20to%20become%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20It%20recently%20received%20a%20huge%20boost%20after%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20backed%20India's%20bid%20for%20the%20permanent%20membership%2C%20days%20after%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20France's%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20made%20a%20similar%20pitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20UNSC%20comprises%20five%20permanent%20members%20and%2010%20non-permanent%20member%20countries%20which%20are%20elected%20for%20a%20two-year%20term%20by%20the%20General%20Assembly.%20The%20five%20permanent%20members%20are%20Russia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20have%20the%20power%20to%20veto%20any%20substantive%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20see%20permanent%20African%20representation%20on%20the%20Council%2C%20Brazil%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Germany%20as%20permanent%20members%2C%20and%20more%20seats%20for%20elected%20members%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Starmer%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728064620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fke6nqj78_john-bol