%20has%20not%20paid%20heed%20to%20the%20community's%20demand%2C%20he%20was%20hopeful%20that%20the%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20would%20address%20their%20concerns%20before%20the%20election%20code%20is%20enforced%20or%20else%20his%20party%20faces%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20NCP%20(SP)%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20appeal%20to%20the%20central%20government%20to%20increase%20the%20quota%20ceiling%20so%20that%20Marathas%20could%20be%20accommodated%2C%20Mr%20Jarange%20said%20he%20supports%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20demand%20for%20increasing%20the%20reservation%20ceiling.%20However%2C%20our%20primary%20demand%20is%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Marathas%20under%20the%20OBC%20quota%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728062040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8ndn18r8_manoj-jarange_625x300_13_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-must-ensure-maratha-quota-before-polls-or-activist-manoj-jaranges-warning-6715938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maratha%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20on%20Friday%20warned%20that%20if%20reservation%20is%20not%20granted%20to%20his%20community%20under%20the%20OBC%20category%20before%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20kicks%20in%20for%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20then%20those%20in%20power%20will%20not%20be%20spared.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20rules%20public%20can%20view%20video%20evidence%20in%20French%20mass%20rape%20trial%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728061410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F