%20preparation%20time%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fswiggy-launches-10-minute-food-delivery-service-bolt-in-six-key-cities-124100401252_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fswiggy-launches-10-minute-food-delivery-service-bolt-in-six-key-cities-124100401252_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fswiggy-launches-10-minute-food-delivery-service-bolt-in-six-key-cities-124100401252_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20Highest%20Gamma%20Ray%20Telescope%20Set%20To%20Peek%20Into%20Universe's%20Secrets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20telescope%20like%20no%20other%2C%20a%20special%20robotic%20eye%20in%20the%20sky%20to%20track%20some%20of%20the%20most%20energetic%20phenomena%20such%20as%20the%20birth%20and%20death%20of%20stars.%20One%20needs%20very%20special%20instruments%20to%20study%20these%20exploding%20stars.%20India%20now%20holds%20the%20honour%20of%20having%20the%20world's%20highest-altitude%20gamma%20ray%20telescope%20situated%20at%204%2C270%20metres%20above%20sea%20level%20and%20it%20has%20the%20largest%20mirror%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20(DAE)%20established%20the%20Major%20Atmospheric%20Cherenkov%20Experiment%20or%20MACE.%20It%20is%20a%20cutting-edge%20gamma%20ray%20telescope%20for%20very%20high%20energy%20astronomy.%20It%20was%20developed%20by%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Centre%20(BARC)%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20is%20installed%20at%20Hanle%2C%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHanle%20is%20like%20heaven%20for%20gamma%20ray%20astronomers%20with%20its%20dark%20skies%2C%20low%20humidity%20and%20almost%20no%20air%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20AK%20Mohanty%2C%20chairman%2C%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%20and%20India's%20nuclear%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20another%20few%20more%20gamma%20ray%20telescopes%20could%20be%20built%20here%2C%20making%20Hanle%20the%20go-to%20place%20for%20global%20astronomers%2C%20some%20with%20international%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20DAE%2C%20the%20MACE%20telescope%2C%20due%20to%20its%20high%20sensitivity%2C%20will%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20gamma%20rays%20from%20supernova%20remnants%2C%20pulsars%20and%20micro-quasars.%20It%20will%20also%20peep%20into%20the%20centres%20of%20distant%20galaxies%20hosting%20supermassive%20blackholes%20and%20will%20be%20able%20to%20discover%20the%20high-energy%20processes%20occurring%20around%20it.%20The%20MACE%20telescope%20will%20be%20used%20to%20search%20for%20dark%20matter%20in%20the%20universe%20and%20unravel%20its%20mysteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20where%20locals%20participated%20in%20large%20numbers%20has%20been%20titled%20'Juley%20Cosmos'.%20%26quot%3BJuley%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20salutation%20used%20by%20Ladakhis%2C%20which%20the%20DAE%20says%20is%20made-in-India%20but%20made%20for%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20situated%20not%20far%20from%20the%20China%20border%2C%20some%20250%20km%20from%20Ladakh's%20capital%20Leh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fuh4dqb2_telescope_625x300_04_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conceptualisation%20and%20design%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Astrophysical%20Sciences%20Division%20of%20BARC.%20The%20MACE%20telescope%20has%20been%20commissioned%20at%20Hanle%2C%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%204%2C270%20metres%20above%20mean%20sea%20level.%20It%20is%20required%20to%20accurately%20position%20the%20large%20mechanical%20structure%2C%20having%20a%2021-metre%20diameter%20reflector%20in%20less%20than%20three%20minutes.%20This%20requires%20careful%20selection%20of%20lightweight%20construction%2C%20approximately%20175%20tonnes%2C%20and%20simultaneously%20maintaining%20high%20strength%20and%20temperature%20endurance.%20Transport%20constraints%20in%20the%20Ladakh%20region%20restrict%20the%20size%20of%20sub-components%20to%20less%20than%202.5%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflector%20surface%20measuring%20over%20350%20square%20metres%20(sqm)%20comprises%20highly%20reflective%20diamond-turned%20custom-built%20metallic%20mirror%20facets%20that%20are%20required%20to%20be%20aligned%20with%20an%20accuracy%20of%202%20mm%20over%20parabolic%20surface.%20The%20camera%20at%20the%20focal%20point%20contains%20a%20number%20of%20photomultiplier%20tubes%20mounted%20with%20specialised%20assembly%20to%20enhance%20light%20collection%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltrafast%20backend%20electronics%20with%20nanosecond%20digitization%20electronics%20is%20optimised%20for%20low-power%20and%20-temperature%20operations.%20Extreme%20weather%20conditions%20restrict%20transport%20to%20six-eight%20months%20a%20year%20and%20affect%20the%20availability%20of%20trained%20personnel%20on%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMACE%20is%20currently%20the%20largest%20Cherenkov%20telescope%20in%20Asia.%20It%20is%20the%20highest%20altitude%20observatory%20among%20similar%20facilities%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20site%20has%20been%20carefully%20chosen%20for%20its%20unique%20scientific%20advantages%20as%20Hanle%20offers%20extremely%20low%20light%20pollution%20required%20for%20gamma%20ray%20observations.%20The%20longitudinal%20advantage%20of%20its%20location%20enables%20MACE%20to%20observe%20sources%20invisible%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMACE%20is%2021%20metres%20in%20diameter%2C%20175%20tonnes%20heavy%2C%20has%20reflector%20area%20of%20356%20sqm%20and%201%2C424%20diamond-turned%20metallic%20mirror%20facets%2C%20712%20actuators%2C%201%2C088%20photo-multiplier%20tubes%2C%20and%2068%20camera%20modules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20inauguration%2C%20Dr%20Annapurni%20Subramaniam%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20that%20is%20the%20host%20agency%20for%20the%20Indian%20Astronomy%20Observatory%20at%20Hanle%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20MACE%20telescope%20is%20an%20engineering%20marvel%20as%20it%20withstands%20the%20very%20high%20winds%20of%20Hanle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20its%20formal%20inauguration%2C%20the%20telescope%20produced%20high-quality%20work%20detecting%20gamma%20ray%20flares%20as%20far%20away%20as%20200%20million%20light%20years%20away%20and%20detected%20during%20observation%20on%20a%20freezing%20December%20night%20in%202022.%20%C2%A0This%20high-altitude%20telescope%20is%20the%20world's%20envy%20and%20India's%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728059820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fknacp45o_hanle-telescope_625x300_04_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-highest-gamma-ray-telescope-set-to-peek-into-universes-secrets-from-ladakh-6717697%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20telescope%20like%20no%20other%2C%20a%20special%20robotic%20eye%20in%20the%20sky%20to%20track%20some%20of%20the%20most%20energetic%20phenomena%20such%20as%20the%20birth%20and%20death%20of%20stars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-highest-gamma-ray-telescope-set-to-peek-into-universes-secrets-from-ladakh-6717697%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20Panday%20starrer%20%E2%80%98CTRL%E2%80%99%20social%20media%20review%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728059575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113947014%2Cimgsize-38080.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fctrl-