ed%20due%20to%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20India%20Rice%20Exporters%20Association%20General%20Secretary%20Ajay%20Bhalotia%20said%20the%20Israel-Iran%20conflict%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Bbasmati%20rice%20industry%20in%20jeopardy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20the%20total%20basmati%20rice%20exported%20from%20India%2C%2025%20percent%20is%20exported%20to%20Iran%20while%2020%20percent%20goes%20to%20Iraq.%20The%20combined%20value%20for%20these%20countries%20is%20more%20than%20two%20million%20tonnes%20whose%20value%20is%20more%20than%20two%20billion%20dollars.%20If%20this%20export%20is%20not%20done%2C%20then%20the%20farmers'%20profit%20in%20the%20fields%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20half%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhalotia%20also%20claimed%20that%20insurance%20companies%20have%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20giving%20insurance%20on%20exports%20to%20Iran%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20possibilities%20of%20export%20to%20Iran%20have%20been%20closed%20due%20to%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20request%20the%20government%20to%20ask%20the%20insurance%20companies%20to%20give%20us%20insurance%20so%20that%20we%20can%20do%20some%20amount%20of%20exports%20to%20Iran%20and%20Iraq%20and%20provide%20fair%20prices%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20their%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%20India%20removed%20the%20floor%20price%20for%20basmati%20rice%20exports%20to%20spur%20orders%20from%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20Americas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20export%20price%20or%20MEP%20posed%20a%20barrier%20to%20exporting%20certain%20basmati%20rice%20grades%2C%20and%20its%20removal%20opened%20up%20opportunities%20for%20global%20buyers%20to%20access%20the%20full%20range%20of%20options%2C%20said%20top%20basmati%20rice%20exporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20leading%20grower%20and%20exporter%20of%20basmati%20rice%20to%20the%20global%20market%2C%20followed%20by%20neighbouring%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Iran-Israel%20Conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20escalated%20after%20the%20latter%20killed%20Hezbollah%20chief%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20in%20an%20airstrike%20last%20week%20that%20flattened%20a%20Beirut%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20fired%20a%20salvo%20of%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20what%20it%20said%20was%20a%20response%20to%20Israel's%20repeated%20targeting%20of%20Iranian%20interests%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missiles%20were%20followed%20by%20a%20sermon%20of%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20when%20told%20a%20huge%20crowd%20in%20Tehran%20that%20Iran%20and%20its%20regional%20allies%20would%20not%20back%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728059040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqnpo1flo_rice-generic-reuters_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-of-iran-israel-conflict-on-indias-basmati-rice-exports-6717567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20grain%20market%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad%2C%20the%20price%20of%20the%20Basmati%201509%20rice%20variety%20has%20decreased%20by%20Rs%20200%20to%20Rs%20300%20per%20quintal%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20because%20the%20exporters%20are%20no%20longer%20coming%20in%20with%20big%20orders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fimpact-of-iran-israel-conflict-on-indias-basmati-rice-exports-6717567%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20appoints%20DS%20Rathore%20as%20CTO%2C%20outgoing%20executive%20named%20'AI%20Fellow'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728058976000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F02%