ected%20through%20their%20mandate.%20The%20confidence%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians%20is%20our%20strength.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20bringing%20more%20structural%20reforms%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BInclusive%20spirit%26quot%3B%20is%20yet%20another%20notable%20factor%20of%20India's%20growth%20story%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20his%20government%20is%20ensuring%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20India's%20growth%20are%20reaped%20by%20everyone.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20increased%20investment%20in%20infrastructure%20on%20an%20unprecedented%20scale%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20India%20has%20made%20process%20reforms%20a%20part%20of%20the%20continuing%20activities%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20global%20rating%20agencies%20and%20multilateral%20organisations%20have%20also%20revised%20their%20growth%20forecasts%20for%20India%20upwards.%20India%20is%20the%20largest%20manufacturer%20of%20two-wheelers%20and%20tractors%2C%20and%20second-largest%20manufacturer%20of%20mobile%20phones.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20moved%20from%20being%20an%20importer%20of%20mobile%20phones%20to%20being%20a%20producer.%20In%20every%20sector%2C%20there%20are%20ample%20investment%20opportunities%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20spoke%20about%20the%20Production-Linked%20Incentive%20(PLI)%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20to%20boost%20manufacturing.%20Investments%20worth%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20crore%20have%20been%20made%20due%20to%20PLI%20scheme%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Atmanirbhar%20and%20Make%20in%20India%20plan%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20PLI%20schemes%20in%2014%20sectors%20in%202020%20to%20make%20Indian%20manufacturers%20globally%20competitive%2C%20attract%20investments%2C%20enhance%20exports%2C%20integrate%20India%20into%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20and%20reduce%20dependency%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETalking%20about%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20'Made%20in%20India'%20chips%20will%20be%20accessible%20to%20the%20world%20once%20the%20five%20plants%20being%20built%20are%20operational.%20The%20government%20has%20so%20far%20approved%20five%20semiconductor%20units%20in%20India%2C%20of%20which%20construction%20in%20two%20sites%20is%20on%2C%20and%20soon%20work%20in%20the%20other%20three%20will%20start.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Institute%20of%20Economic%20Growth%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%2C%20is%20hosting%20the%20third%20edition%20of%20Kautilya%20Economic%20Conclave%20with%20the%20theme%20'The%20Indian%20Era'.%20The%20conclave%20from%20October%204%20to%206%20brings%20together%20close%20to%20150%20national%20and%20international%20academicians%20and%20policy%20makers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728057540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F910jcpm8_narendra-modi_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finclusive-spirit-notable-factor-of-indias-growth-story-says-pm-narendra-modi-10-points-6717462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20described%20India%20as%20a%20sweet%20spot%20amid%20global%20uncertainty%2C%20which%20is%20also%20going%20through%20transformational%20changes%20to%20sustain%20its%20high%20economic%20growth.%20He%20said%20the%20optimism%20around%20India%20is%20the%20result%20of%20good%20reforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finclusive-spirit-notable-factor-of-indias-growth-story-says-pm-narendra-modi-10-points-6717462%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govinda's%20dad%20lost%20all%20money%20after%20his%20film%20flopped%20at%20BO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%