22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECiting%20his%20visit%20to%20violence-hit%20Manipur%2C%20his%20strong%20attacks%20on%20the%20government%20over%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20issue%20and%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20removal%20of%20indexation%20benefits%20on%20long-term%20capital%20gains%2C%20which%20was%20partially%20rolled%20back%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20of%20the%20voiceless%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20first%20100%20days%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20long%20post%20on%20X%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Pawan%20Khera%20listed%20some%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20achievements%20on%20taking%20up%20his%20first%20constitutional%20post%2020%20years%20after%20he%20entered%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20June%2C%20after%20the%20party%20became%20eligible%20to%20get%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20post%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2010%20years%2C%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20should%20hold%20the%20office.%20The%20Congress%20leader%2C%20who%20had%20won%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20constituencies%20with%20margins%20of%20over%203.5%20lakh%20votes%2C%20was%20said%20to%20be%20reluctant%2C%20but%20had%20given%20in%20to%20the%20party's%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Gandhi%20completed%20100%20days%2C%20Mr%20Khera%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20championing%20the%20cause%20of%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20to%20opposing%20unjust%20government%20policies%2C%20he%20(Mr%20Gandhi)%20has%20consistently%20stood%20up%20for%20the%20marginalised%20and%20the%20oppressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20visited%20violence-hit%20Manipur%2C%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20in%20July%20and%20not%20only%20went%20to%20relief%20camps%20and%20interacted%20with%20people%20there%2C%20but%20also%20met%20delegates%20and%20raised%20the%20state's%20issues%20in%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20month%2C%20when%20the%20paper%20leak%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%20exams%20and%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20other%20entrance%20tests%20had%20led%20to%20large-scale%20protests%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20led%20the%20charge%20in%20Parliament%2C%20attacking%20the%20government%20and%20pushing%20for%20accountability%2C%20alleging%20that%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20was%20blaming%20everyone%20but%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELateral%20Entry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khera%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20opposed%20lateral%20advertisements%20for%20recruitment%20for%2045%20posts%20in%20the%20bureaucracy%20in%20August%2C%20which%20the%20government%20had%20later%20withdrawn.%20The%20Congress%20had%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20it%20was%20another%20step%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20to%20undermine%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20loco%20pilots'%20working%20conditions%2C%20highlighting%20the%20impact%20on%20train%20safety.%20Media%20attention%20followed%2C%20ensuring%20the%20issue%20couldn't%20be%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khera%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20stood%20firm%20against%20the%20Broadcast%20Bill%20aimed%20at%20stifling%20independent%20media%20voices.%20Thanks%20to%20Rahul's%20leadership%2C%20the%20bill%20was%20junked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20point%20highlighted%20by%20Mr%20Khera%20was%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20speaking%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20removal%20of%20indexation%20benefits%20for%20Long%20Term%20Capital%20Gains%20tax%20in%20the%20Budget.%20The%20benefit%20was%20restored%20for%20properties%20bought%20before%20July%2023%2C%202024%2C%20after%20widespread%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20also%20pointed%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20strong%20opposition%20of%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%20for%20recruitment%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20his%20%26quot%3Bdefence%20of%20India's%20secular%20values%26quot%3B%20by%20pushing%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20panel%20for%20review%20and%20his%20leadership%20on%20the%20caste%20census%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Listened%20To%20Grievances'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20chose%20to%20stand%20with%20victims%20of%20tragic%20incidents%20over%20attending%20high-profile%20events%2C%20showing%20his%20commitment%20to%20common%20people%20over%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khera%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20100%20days%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%2C%20listening%20to%20the%20grievances%20of%20farmers%2C%20labourers%2C%20loco%20pilots%2C%20and%20manual%20scavengers%2C%20ensuring%20their%20voices%20are%20heard%20and%20their%20issues%20are%20brought%20to%20the%20forefront%20in%20Parliament%2C%20making%20him%20a%20true%20Voice%20of%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728049860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpj7fu35_rahul-gandhi_625x300_01_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-has-congress-on-100-days-as-leader-of-opposition-6716550%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Citing%20his%20visit%20to%20Manipur%20and%20his%20strong%20attacks%20on%20the%20government%20over%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20issue%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20of%20the%20voiceless%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20first%20100%20days%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-has-congress-on-100-days-as-leader-of-opposi