%20earlier%20this%20week%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Vardhman%20group%20SP%20Oswal%2C%20was%20conned%20by%20fraudsters%20impersonating%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20in%20a%20fake%20courtroom%20setting%20over%20a%20video%20call.%20The%20cyber%20crooks%20convinced%20him%20that%20he%20was%20charged%20with%20money%20laundering%20and%20the%20court%20%26quot%3Bordered%26quot%3B%20him%20to%20deposit%20Rs.%207.3%20crore%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20modus%20operandi%20took%20even%20the%20police%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tragic%20incident%20this%20week%2C%20an%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20teacher%20was%20digitally%20arrested%20for%20four%20hours%20and%20forced%20to%20shell%20out%20money%20%26quot%3Bto%20save%20her%20daughter%20from%20prosecution%26quot%3B%20for%20being%20part%20of%20a%20sex%20racket.%20The%20teacher's%20son%20busted%20the%20con%2C%20but%20she%20suffered%20a%20heart%20attack%20and%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20con%2C%20cybercriminals%20are%20improvising%2C%20innovating%20and%20improving%20on%20their%20techniques%20of%20preying%20on%20victims%2C%20convincing%20them%20to%20fork%20over%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20and%20managing%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20going%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20is%20'digital%20arrest'%3F%20Scammers%20posing%20as%20police%20or%20prosecuting%20officials%20contact%20marks%20online%20and%20virtually%20'arrest'%20them%20for%20hours%20or%20even%20days%20in%20extreme%20incidents.%20The%20victims%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20switch%20off%20their%20video%20camera%20or%20microphone%20or%20contact%20anyone%20outside%20the%20room.%20The%20marks%20fall%20for%20it%2C%20be%20it%20a%20middle-aged%20teacher%20or%20an%2082-year-old%20industrialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModus%20operandi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECybercriminals%20swindled%20Rs%201%2C750%20crore%20from%20Indians%20in%20January-April%2C%20during%20which%207.4%20lakh%20cybercrime%20complaints%20were%20lodged%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20alarming%20rise%20led%20to%20the%20government%20disconnecting%202.17%20crore%20mobile%20connections%20and%20blocking%202.26%20lakh%20mobile%20handsets%20procured%20on%20forged%20documents%20and%20used%20to%20commit%20cyber-fraud.%20This%20step%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20temporary%20halt%20to%20phishing%20but%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20lasting%20deterrent.%20Cybercrooks%20stay%20a%20step%20ahead%2C%20eventually%20finding%20workarounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20the%20digital%20arrest%20call%20was%20a%20video%20WhatsApp%20call%20from%20an%20unknown%20number.%20When%20the%20mark%20picks%20up%2C%20a%20nude%20woman%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20screen%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20By%20the%20time%20realisation%20dawns%20on%20the%20victim%2C%20the%20call%20gets%20disconnected.%20Next%20comes%20the%20blackmail%20call%2C%20with%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20victim%20with%20a%20nude%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technique%20has%20evolved%20into%20an%20elaborate%20scam%20with%20the%20scammers%20using%20technology%20tools%20replicating%20real-life%20sets%20to%20play%20with%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20even%20educated%20people%20susceptible%20to%20digital%20arrest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20arrest%20doesn't%20exist%20in%20law.%20Criminals%20play%20with%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20using%20fake%20allegations%20and%20threatening%20them%20with%20consequences%20such%20as%20arrest.%20This%20intimidating%20trap%20coupled%20with%20isolation%20leads%20to%20victims%20shelling%20out%20money%20to%20save%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Seemant%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20psychological%20manipulation%20using%20AI.%20Even%20AI-driven%20sobbing%20voices%20of%20family%20members%20are%20used%20to%20convince%20victims.%20Use%20of%20technology%2C%20police%20uniforms%2C%20DP%20of%20police%20officers%2C%20are%20innovations%20done%20by%20criminals%20to%20dupe%20ignorant%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Spot%20A%20Digital%20Arrest%20Scam%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20experts%20advise%20calm%20and%20caution.%20Awareness%20about%20law%20enforcement%20is%20a%20big%20plus.%20%C2%A0Ahmedabad-based%20cyber%20security%20consultant%20Sunny%20Vaghela%20has%20these%20tips%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStay%20calm%20and%20sceptical%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENever%20take%20a%20video%20call%2C%20document%2C%20or%20phone%20number%20at%20face%20value%2C%20even%20if%20the%20number%20appears%20legitimate%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVerify%20the%20caller's%20identity%20by%20contacting%20the%20official%20agency%20directly%20through%20verified%20channels%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20aware%20that%20real%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20will%20never%20demand%20money%20over%20the%20phone%20or%20via%20video%20calls%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETaking%20time%20to%20verify%20any%20request%20before%20acting%20out%20of%20fear%20is%20key%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BTo%20avoid%20falling%20victim%2C%20it's%20essential%20to%20remain%20calm%20and%20sceptical.%20Never%20trust%20a%20video%20call%2C%20document%2C%20or%20phone%20number%20at%20face%20value%2C%20even%20if%20the%20number%20appears%20legitimate%20online.%20Always%20verify%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20caller%20by%20contacting%20the%20official%20agency%20directly%20through%20verified%20channels.%20Real%20law%20enforcement%20will%20never%20demand%20money%20over%20the%20phone%20or%20via%20video%20calls.%20Taking%20time%20to%20verify%20any%20request%20before%20acting%2C%20rather%20than%20responding%20out%20of%20fear%2C%20is%20key.%20Public%20awareness%20and%20education%20on%20these%20tactics%20are%20crucial%20to%20prevent%20individuals%20from%20falling%20prey%20to%20such%20sophisticated%20frauds%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sunny%20Vaghela%2C%20Ahmedabad-based%20cyber%20security%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20Needed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20scored%2098.49%20out%20of%20100%20in%20the%20Global%20Cybersecurity%20Index%20(GCI)%202024%20and%20joined%20the%20'role-model'%20countries%20by%20achieving%20Tier%201%20status.%20This%20is%20about%20a%20mechanism%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20victims%20should%20be%20careful%20too.%20For%20those%20who%20are%20conned%2C%20the%20government%20has%20launched%20a%20pan-India%20helpline%201930%20so%20that%20best%20efforts%20are%20made%20to%20trace%20the%20accused%20and%20recover%20the%20stolen%20money.%20%26quot%3BIn%20police%20terminology%2C%20if%20the%20money%20has%20gone%20through%20multiple%20layers%20already%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20recover.%20Timely%20reporting%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20the%20risks%20of%20innovative%20types%20of%20cyber%20fraud%20and%20its%20latest%20manifestation%2C%20the%20digital%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BDigital%20arrest%20scams%20are%20highly%20deceptive%2C%20with%20criminals%20going%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20impersonate%20law%20enforcement.%20They%20often%20make%20video%20calls%2C%20adding%20a%20visual%20element%20to%20the%20fraud%20to%20enhance%20the%20scam's%20credibility.%20Combined%20with%20fake%20arrest%20warrants%20and%20legal%20notices%2C%20this%20creates%20a%20highly%20convincing%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sunny%20Vaghela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20our%20country%20need%20to%20be%20agile%20in%20anticipating%20and%20thwarting%20new-age%20crooks%20who%20are%20adept%20at%20disarming%20and%20fleecing%20people%20using%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20common%20person%20does%20not%20have%20much%20knowledge%20about%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20because%20they%20have%20never%20dealt%20with%20them.%20Since%20their%20loved%20ones%20are%20seemingly%20involved%2C%20they%20try%20to%20buy%20their%20way%20out%20of%20the%20crisis.%20That's%20why%20educated%20people%20with%20financial%20resources%20are%20also%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20police%20officer%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeep%20fake%20technology%20has%20already%20proved%20to%20be%20effective%20in%20scamming%20people.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20the%20digital%20arrest%20scam%20will%20incorporate%20deep%20fakes%20to%20swindle%20more%20and%20more%20people.%20International%20cybercrime%20syndicates%20are%20collaborating%2C%20innovating%2C%20extorting%20and%20sharing%20the%20spoils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20needs%20a%20survival%20guide.%20The%20government%20must%20teach%20cyber%20awareness%20in%20schools%2C%20rope%20in%20best-in-class%20technical%20experts%20and%20use%20the%20services%20of%20ethical%20hackers.%20Coordination%20between%20various%20international%2C%20central%20and%20state%20agencies%20will%20be%20key%20to%20creating%20public%20awareness%20and%20building%20deterrence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728048720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7emhd6j8_cyber-crime-generic_625x300_02_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcyber-crooks-baffle-police-with-audacious-tricks-like-digital-arrest-6716365%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cybercriminals%20are%20baffling%20even%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20with%20their%20audacious%20tricks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcyber-crooks-baffle-police-with-audacious-tricks-like-digital-arrest-6716365%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ace%20Aviation%20acquires%20aircraft%20from%20market%20as%20Jet%20Airways%20deal%20faces%20delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe