ml%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-wilmar-sees-q2-standalone-revenue-to-rise-16-on-higher-sales-volumes-124100400895_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20To%20Visit%20Pak%2C%20First%20Foreign%20Minister%20There%20Since%20Sushma%20Swaraj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20will%20visit%20Pakistan%20later%20this%20month%20to%20attend%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20to%20do%20so%20in%20nine%20years.%20The%20last%20visit%20was%20by%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20in%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Ministry%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20will%20lead%20a%20delegation%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20a%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20Council%20of%20Heads%20of%20Government%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20will%20lead%20our%20delegation%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20SCO%20summit%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Islamabad%20on%20October%2015%20and%2016%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%2C%20emphasising%20that%20the%20visit%20will%20be%20limited%20to%20attending%20the%20summit.%20Pakistan%20had%20invited%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20the%20meeting%20in%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20send%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20summit%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20one%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20given%20the%20chill%20in%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20since%20the%20Pulwama%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20February%202019%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Balakot%20air%20strikes%2C%20in%20which%20India%20targeted%20a%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20training%20camp.%20The%20relationship%20got%20even%20more%20strained%20after%20Pakistan%20vociferously%20opposed%20India's%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20slammed%20Pakistan's%20interference%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20reiterated%20that%20it%20is%20an%20internal%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20last%20week%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20had%20warned%20Pakistan%20that%20its%20policy%20of%20cross-border%20terrorism%20could%20never%20succeed%20and%20also%20alluded%20to%20its%20economic%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20countries%20get%20left%20behind%20due%20to%20circumstances%20beyond%20their%20control.%20But%20some%20make%20conscious%20choices%20with%20disastrous%20consequences.%20A%20premier%20example%20is%20our%20neighbour%2C%20Pakistan.%20Unfortunately%2C%20their%20misdeeds%20affect%20others%20as%20well%2C%20especially%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplay%20Of%20Commitment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20all%20of%20this%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20will%20attend%20the%20summit%20in%20the%20country%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20display%20of%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20SCO%20which%2C%20it%20believes%2C%20has%20been%20playing%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20boosting%20regional%20security%20cooperation.%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20had%20visited%20Pakistan%20in%202015%20to%20attend%20a%20conference%20on%20Afghanistan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20India%2C%20the%20SCO%20has%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20Tajikistan%20and%20Uzbekistan%20as%20member%20countries%20and%20is%20an%20influential%20economic%20and%20security%20bloc%20as%20well%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20transregional%20international%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20was%20founded%20at%20a%20summit%20in%20Shanghai%20in%202001%20by%20the%20presidents%20of%20Russia%2C%20China%2C%20the%20Kyrgyz%20Republic%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Tajikistan%20and%20Uzbekistan%20and%20India%20was%20an%20observer%20country%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202005.%20It%20became%20a%20permanent%20member%2C%20along%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20in%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20organisation%20in%202023%20and%20hosted%20the%20SCO%20summit%20in%20the%20virtual%20format%20in%20July%20of%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20Council%20of%20Heads%20of%20Government%20conclave%2C%20which%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20will%20be%20attending%2C%20is%20the%20second-highest%20platform%20in%20the%20grouping%20while%20the%20Heads%20of%20State%20Summit%20is%20the%20top-most%20forum%20and%20is%20generally%20attended%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728046980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvosli4u8_s-jaishankar_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsco-meet-pakistan-external-affairs-minister-s-jaishankar-to-visit-pak-first-foreign-minister-there-since-sushma-swaraj-6715952%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20will%20visit%20Pakistan%20later%20this%20month%20to%20attend%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20to%20do%20so%20in%20nine%20years.%20The%20last%20visit%20was%20by%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20in%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsco-meet-pakistan-external-affairs-minister-s-jaishankar-to-visit-pak-first-foreign-minister-there-since-sushma-swaraj-6715952%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20might%20happen%20next%20with%20conflict%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3F%2010%20experts%20share%20their%20analysis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728046315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fd85d%2Flive%2F