2C%20the%20team%20of%20researchers%20found%20plant%20life%20-%20mostly%20mosses%20-%20and%20said%20the%20green%20cover%20has%20increased%2010-fold%20over%20the%20past%20four%20decades%20or%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20published%20on%20Friday%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41561-024-01564-5%5C%22%3ENature%20Geoscience%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20meagre%200.4%20square%20miles%20in%201986%2C%20the%20vegetation%20cover%20reached%20almost%205%20square%20miles%20in%202021%2C%20the%20study%20found.%20In%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20-%20from%202016%20to%202021%20-%20accelerated%20by%20more%20than%2030%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20confirm%20that%20the%20influence%20of%20anthropogenic%20climate%20change%20has%20no%20limit%20in%20its%20reach%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Roland%2C%20a%20study%20author%20and%20environmental%20scientist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Exeter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F10%2F04%2Fclimate%2Fantarctica-greening-vegetation-satellite-images%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BEven%20on%20the%20Antarctic%20Peninsula%20-%20this%20most%20extreme%2C%20remote%20and%20isolated%20'wilderness'%20region%20-%20the%20landscape%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20these%20effects%20are%20visible%20from%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20landscape%20is%20almost%20entirely%20snow%2C%20these%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20green%20cover%20has%20grown%20dramatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20conference%20in%20Chile%20in%20August%2C%20nearly%201%2C500%20academics%2C%20researchers%20and%20scientists%20discussed%20whether%20the%20extreme%20climate%20events%20events%20meant%20Antarctica%20had%20reached%20a%20tipping%20point%2C%20or%20a%20point%20of%20accelerated%20and%20irreversible%20sea%20ice%20loss%20from%20the%20West%20Antarctic%20ice%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20see%20the%20same%20rise%20in%20CO2%20over%20thousands%20of%20years%2C%20and%20now%20it's%20happened%20in%20100%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Liz%20Keller%2C%20a%20paleoclimate%20specialist%20from%20the%20Victoria%20University%20of%20Wellington%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntarctica%2C%20the%20coldest%20place%20on%20Earth%2C%20has%20witnessed%20severe%20extreme%20heat%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20summer%20months%20this%20year%2C%20the%20average%20temperature%20in%20the%20continent%20climbed%20up%20to%2050%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20above%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20temperatures%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20Antarctica%20reached%20up%20to%2070%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20above%20normal%2C%20the%20most%20extreme%20temperature%20variation%20ever%20recorded%20in%20the%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728043920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjeod7c18_antarctica-turning-green_625x300_04_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fantarctica-turning-green-at-an-alarming-rate-says-study-6715700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20a%20meagre%200.4%20square%20miles%20in%201986%2C%20the%20vegetation%20cover%20reached%20almost%205%20square%20miles%20in%202021%2C%20the%20study%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fantarctica-turning-green-at-an-alarming-rate-says-study-6715700%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%20didn't%20have%20to%20happen'%3A%20Wife%20of%20man%20killed%20at%20Trump%20rally%20struggles%20with%20loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728043291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4151%2Flive%2F5d95e5b0-823f-11ef-822c-a50726bfda2e.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20jez2dvw8o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Corey%20Comperatore%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20Trump%20rally%20assassination%20attempt.%20His%20wife%20is%20furious%20at%20the%20security%20failures%20that%20led%20to%20his%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A570%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20jez2dvw8o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20jez2dvw8o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc20jez2dvw8o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20To%20Travel%20To%20Pak%2C%20Last%20Foreign%20Minister%20Visit%20Was%20In%202015%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20will%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20a%20conclave%20of%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20in%20mid-October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20to%20visit%20Pakistan%20was%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%20She%20had%20travelled%20to%20Islamabad%20in%20December%202015%20to%20attend%20a%20conference%20on%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20is%20hosting%20the%20SCO%20Council%20of%20Heads%20of%20Government%20(CHG)%20meeting%20on%20October%2015%20and%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20will%20lead%20our%20delegation%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20SCO%20summit%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Islamabad%20on%20October%2015%20and%2016%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%20at%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20clarified%20that%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20is%20travelling%20to%20Pakistan%20only%20to%20attend%20the%20SCO%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Pakistan%20invited%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20the%20SCO's%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20visit%20to%20Pakistan%20assumes%20significance%20as%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20decision%20on%20New%20Delhi's%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20send%20the%20senior%20minister%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20display%20of%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20SCO%20which%20has%20been%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20boosting%20regional%20security%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20after%20India's%20warplanes%20pounded%20a%20Jaish-e-Mohammed%20terrorist%20training%20camp%20in%20Balakot%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20February%202019%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Pulwama%20terror%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20further%20deteriorated%20after%20India%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20special%20powers%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20it%20desires%20normal%20neighbourly%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20while%20insisting%20that%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20Islamabad%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20free%20of%20terror%20and%20hostility%20for%20such%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20council%20of%20heads%20of%20government%20conclave%20is%20the%20second-highest%20platform%20in%20the%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20heads%20of%20state%20summit%20is%20the%20top%20most%20forum%20in%20the%20grouping%20that%20is%20generally%20attended%20by%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%2C%20comprising%20India%2C%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan%2C%20Tajikistan%20and%20Uzbekistan%2C%20is%20an%20influential%20economic%20and%20security%20bloc%20that%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20transregional%20international%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20SCO%20last%20year.%20It%20hosted%20the%20SCO%20summit%20in%20the%20virtual%20format%20in%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20association%20with%20the%20SCO%20began%20in%202005%20as%20an%20observer%20country.%20It%20became%20a%20full%20member%20state%20of%20SCO%20at%20the%20Astana%20summit%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20shown%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20deepening%20its%20security-related%20cooperation%20with%20the%20SCO%20and%20its%20Regional%20Anti-Terrorism%20Structure%20(RATS)%2C%20which%20specifically%20deals%20with%20issues%20relating%20to%20security%20and%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCO%20was%20founded%20at%20a%20summit%20in%20Shanghai%20in%202001%20by%20the%20presidents%20of%20Russia%2C%20China%2C%20the%20Kyrgyz%20Republic%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Tajikistan%20and%20Uzbekistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20became%20its%20permanent%20member%20along%20with%20India%20in%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728043140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjvjnd69o_dr-s-jaishankar_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-to-travel-to-pak-last-foreign-minister-visit-was-in-2015-6715527%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20will%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20attend%20a%20conclave%20of%20the%20Shanghai%20Cooperation%20Organisation%20(SCO)%20in%20mid-October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fs-jaishankar-to-travel-to-pak-last-foreign-minister-visit-was-in-2015-6715527%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7