0love%20with%20it%20and%20learnt%20how%20to%20swim%20in%20the%20sea%20with%20my%20friends.%20But%20I%20also%20saw%20many%20people%20drowning%20in%20the%20sea%20and%20that%20left%20a%20real%20impression%20on%20me.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20wanted%20a%20job%20where%20I%20could%20save%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Drishti%20Marine%20was%20operational%20in%202008%2C%20Shashikant%20was%20a%20lifeguard%20working%20for%20another%20company%20contracted%20by%20the%20tourism%20department%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267418%2Fgoa-government-school-robotics-coding-scheme-first-india-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoa%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20there%20was%20little%20to%20no%20coordination%20in%20rescue%20efforts.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20the%20people%20in%20charge%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20I%20had%20swam%20out%20into%20the%20sea%20to%20rescue%20someone.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20proper%20equipment%20like%20a%20surfboard%2C%20walkie-talkie%2C%20lifeguard%20jeep%2C%20or%20jet-ski%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20coordination%2C%20equipment%2C%20and%20professionalism%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20lack%20of%20beach%20safety%20and%20the%20number%20of%20drowning%20deaths%20Goa%20saw.%20Matters%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202007%20when%20the%20state%20unfortunately%20saw%20200%20people%20drown%20off%20the%20coastline%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20Somani%2C%20founder%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Drishti%20Marine%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CFollowing%20the%20events%20of%202007%2C%20the%20State%20Government%20was%20prompted%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%2