Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20Drishti%20in%20July%202008%2C%20they%20put%20me%20through%20a%2045-day%20training%20course%20where%20I%20learned%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20lifeguarding%20and%20how%20to%20use%20the%20new%20equipment%20given%20to%20us.%20There%20was%20a%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20safety%20here.%20In%20my%20previous%20job%2C%20we%20would%20get%20no%20backup%20during%20rescue%20efforts.%20Now%2C%20whenever%20we%20go%20out%20on%20a%20rescue%2C%20we%20are%20supported%20by%20jet%20skis%2C%20backup%20lifeguards%2C%20etc.%20Also%2C%20we%20receive%20continuous%20training%20and%20have%20reorientation%20sessions%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20methods%20and%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBraving%20the%20waves%3A%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Drishti%20Marine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Drishti%20becoming%20the%20designated%20agency%20to%20provide%20lifeguard%20services%20also%20prompted%20Ashwin%20Ghag%2C%20a%20former%20national-level%20swimmer%2C%20to%20leave%20Pune%20for%20Goa%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%201999%20to%202008%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20swimming%20coach%20for%20children%20in%20Pune%2C%20after%20which%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20senior%20lifeguard.%20Before%20my%20swimming%20coach%20and%20lifeguard%20career%2C%20I%20was%20a%20national-level%20swimmer.%20I%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20father%20to%20become%20a%20lifeguard.%20Watching%20him%20work%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159192%2Fpune-drowning-lives-raju%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20me%20to%20become%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ashwin%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20senior%20lifeguard%20at%20Drishti%20Marine%20currently%20posted%20on%20the%20popular%20and%20crowded%20Calangute%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%