%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAURUS%20%E2%80%94%20a%20self-driving%2C%20AI-powered%20robot%20that%20patrols%20non-swim%20zones%2C%20provides%20logistical%20support%2C%20and%20assists%20lifesavers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20has%20also%20integrated%20%E2%80%98advanced%20technology%E2%80%99%20to%20enhance%20the%20efforts%20of%20their%20lifeguards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20sister%20concern%2C%20Drishti%20Works%2C%20has%20developed%20AURUS%20%E2%80%94%20a%20self-driving%2C%20AI-powered%20robot%20that%20patrols%20non-swim%20zones%2C%20provides%20logistical%20support%2C%20and%20assists%20lifesavers%20in%20making%20public%20safety%20announcements%20in%20multiple%20languages.%20It%20works%20alongside%20TRITON%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI-driven%20monitoring%20system%20that%20offers%20comprehensive%20beach%20surveillance%2C%20spots%20tourists%20in%20distress%20in%20the%20water%20over%20long%20distances%2C%20and%20aids%20lifesavers%20in%20emergencies.%20Both%20AURUS%20and%20TRITON%20are%20currently%20deployed%20at%20Miramar%20beach%20in%20Panaji%20and%20operated%20by%20our%20%E2%80%98tech%20lifesavers%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20lives%20and%20challenges%20of%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20lifeguards%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Drishti%20Marine%20became%20the%20custodian%20of%20beach%20safety%20in%20Goa%20in%202008%2C%20their%20lifeguards%20have%20rescued%20over%207%2C700%20people%2C%20including%20locals%2C%20and%20domestic%2C%20and%20international%20tourists%2C%20claims%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20also%20trained%20responders%20for%20marine%20life%20strandings%2C%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20Forest%20Department%20and%20NGOs%20focused%20on%20marine%20welfare.%20A%20recent%20notable%20rescue%20occurred%20over%20the%20Independence%20Day%20weekend%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Drishti%20lifesavers%20(lifeguards)%20rescued%20nine%20fishermen%20after%20their%20boat%20capsized%20off%20Rajbagh%20Beach%20in%20South%20Goa%2C%20demonstrating%20their%20ability%20to%20handle%20mass%20rescues%20in%20extreme%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20goes%20on%20to%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20professional%20training%20that%20the%20Drishti%20lifeguards%20receive%2C%20which%20saves%20them%20from%20many%20dangers%20associated%20with%20saving%20people%20from%20drowning%20at%20sea%2C%20the%20challenges%20they%20encounter%20are%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20Shashikant%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20are%20drowning%2C%20they%20panic.%20When%20you%20directly%20engage%20with%20a%20victim%20of%20drowning%2C%20there%20is%20always%20the%20danger%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20drag%20you%20into%20the%20water%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20lifeguards%2C%20we%20are%20told%20to%20first%20deploy%20a%20rescue%20tube%20or%20board%2C%20which%20the%20person%20drowning%20can%20hold%20on%20to%2C%20turn%20them%20towards%20the%20shore%2C%20clear%20up%20their%20airways%2C%20and%20push%20them%20towards%20the%20shore.%20But%20on%20occasions%20you%20come%20across%20drunk%20people%20who%20have%20swam%20too%20far%20off%20shore%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20get%20them%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20rescue%20tube%20or%20board.%20With%20drunk%20people%2C%20we%20try%20to%20identify%20as%20many%20of%20them%20as%20possible%20and%20send%20out%20teams%20to%20evacuate%20them%20from%20the%20beach%20itself%2C%20or%20push%20them%20as%20far%20as%20away%20as%20possible%20from%20the%20shoreline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%2C%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20done%20484%20rescues%20to%20date%2C%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20having%20rescue%20equipment%2C%20a%20drowning%20person%E2%80%99s%20first%20instinct%20is%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20rescuer%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20in%20a%20state%20of%20panic.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20occasions%20when%20the%20rip%20current%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20it%20takes%20six%20or%20seven%20people%20with%20it.%20This%20happens%20because%20one%20person%20tries%20to%20save%20the%20other%20but%20encounters%20strong%20rip%20currents.%20Handling%20these%20situations%20is%20challenging%20and%20you%20need%20more%20than%20one%20lifeguard%20and%20multiple%20equipment%20to%20save%20them.%20I%20was%20part%20of%20a%20rescue%20effort%20where%20we%20saved%20seven%20people%20at%20once.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fu1vobuGfnMo%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20also%20agrees%20that%20dealing%20with%20drunk%20people%20drowning%20at%20sea%20is%20challenging.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20them%20are%20so%20drunk%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20realise%20that%20they%20have%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20a%20rescue%20board.%20Thanks%20to%20years%20of%20experience%20and%20training%2C%20we%20have%20learnt%20how%20to%20handle%20such%20situations.%20The%20trouble%20with%20drunk%20people%20is%20that%20sometimes%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20strength%20to%20get%20their%20torso%20on%20top%20of%20the%20rescue%20board.%20We%20have%20to%20help%20them%20get%20on%20top%20of%20the%20surfboard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20before%20deploying%20the%20surfboard%20and%20pushing%20them%20up%20on%20the%20surfboard%2C%20we%20have%20to%20gauge%20the%20strength%20and%20movement%20of%20the%20waves%20and%20time%20our%20efforts%20properly.%20Now%2C%20if%20I%20jump%20into%20the%20water%20without%20timing%20it%20properly%2C%20the%20rescue%20board%20may%20get%20washed%20away%20onto%20the%20shore%20and%20then%20I%20have%20to%20push%20and%20carry%20the%20drowning%20person%20back%20without%20the%20rescue%20equipment.%20My%20job%20is%20to%20get%20the%20person%20who%20is%20drowning%20on%20top%20of%20the%20rescue%20board%20and%20drag%20them%20back%20to%20shore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20training%2C%20Ashwin%20notes%20that%20there%20are%20occasions%20when%20the%20sea%20just%20overwhelms%20you%20with%20massive%20waves%20and%20strong%20currents.%20%E2%80%9CBesides%20these%20rip%20currents%2C%20you%20are%20also%20dealing%20with%20strong%20plunging%20waves%20that%20roll%20over%20victims%20of%20drowning.%20On%20these%20occasions%2C%20victims%20are%20often%20dragged%20200%20to%20400%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20shoreline.%20As%20trained%20lifeguards%2C%20we%20know%20how%20to%20swim%20and%20navigate%20past%20these%20plunging%20waves%20and%20rip%20currents.%20For%20tourists%2C%20however%2C%20if%20they%20get%20rolled%20under%20these%20massive%20plunging%20waves%2C%20they%20end%20up%20taking%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20seawater.%20In%20these%20scenarios%2C%20we%20have%20to%20deploy%20jet%20skis%20to%20rescue%20them%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20single-person%20rescue%2C%20we%20often%20use%20a%20rescue%20tube.%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%20one%20person%2C%20we%20use%20a%20surf%2Frescue%20board.%20But%20our%20fastest%20equipment%20are%20jet%20skis%2C%20and%20these%20are%20particularly%20useful%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20when%20the%20rip%20currents%20are%20strongest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashikant%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20challenge%20we%20encounter%20is%20uncooperative%20tourists%2C%20especially%20from%20foreign%20countries.%20When%20they%20visit%20Goa%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20see%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20they%20get%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20waters%20here%20are%20calm.%20What%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20realise%20is%20the%20power%20of%20strong%20rip%20currents%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20get%20into%20arguments%20with%20tourists%20and%20have%20to%20call%20the%20police%20to%20disperse%20them%20away%20from%20points%20where%20they%20can%20potentially%20drown.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20best%20efforts%2C%20however%2C%20there%20are%20rare%20occasions%20when%20people%20drown%20to%20death.%20How%20do%20lifeguards%20deal%20with%20this%20devastation%3F%20With%20a%20resigned%20look%20on%2C%20Shashikant%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20just%20human%2C%20and%20not%20gods.%20We%20do%20everything%20to%20save%20a%20life%20but%20sometimes%20God%20has%20other%20plans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20lifesaving%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20job%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20calling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drishti%20Marine%20chairperson%20Rajiv%20Somani%20on%20the%20left.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDrishti-Marine-Rajiv-Somani-1727449328-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367918%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDrishti%20Marine%20chairperson%20Rajiv%20Somani%20on%20the%20left.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20given%20the%20risks%20they%20undertake%2C%20what%20sort%20of%20monetary%20compensation%20and%20social%20security%20do%20their%20lifeguards%20receive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20young%20lifesavers%20start%20their%20careers%20with%20a%20salary%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%2018%2C000%20per%20month.%20Lifesavers%20in%20senior%20positions%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20month.%20Lifesavers%20are%20provided%20with%20legally%20mandated%20insurance%20policies%2C%20including%20workmen%E2%80%99s%20compensation%2C%20and%20medical%20insurance.%20Additionally%2C%20those%20who%20marry%20are%20eligible%20for%20benefits%2C%20such%20as%20LIC%20policies%20and%20fixed%20deposits%20for%20the%20couple.%20The%20organisation%20also%20offers%20a%20referral%20programme.%20Volunteers%20interested%20in%20pursuing%20lifesaving%20as%20a%20vocation%20are%20offered%20Rs%2018%2C000%20for%20a%20three-month%20assessment%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drishtimarine.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrishti%20Marine%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727686756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FImage-2-1727448639.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20its%20inception%20in%202008%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%E2%80%99s%20450-plus%20strong%20force%20of%20lifeguards%20has%20saved%20approximately%207%2C700%20lives%20from%20drowning%20off%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20coastline%2C%20claims%20its%20chairperson%20Rajiv%20Somani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367889%2Fdrishti-marine-lifeguards-saving-lives-from-drowning-beaches-goa-government%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Punished%20for%20Her%20Deafness%2C%20Rupmani%20Chhetri%20Now%20Empowers%20Thousands%20With%20the%20Signable%20App%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Darjeeling%2C%20Rupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications%2C%20felt%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20loneliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Rupmani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20child%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20I%20was%20the%20only%20Deaf%20person%20in%20the%20world.%20With%20no%20awareness%20of%20sign%20language%2C%20I%20experienced%20discrimination%20with%20various%20labels%20placed%20on%20me%20because%20of%20my%20Deafness.%20I%20was%20excluded%20from%20family%20activities%20and%20conversation%20and%20struggled%20in%20school%2C%20as%20teachers%20would%20speak%20and%20I%20could%20not%20hear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20adequate%20school%20for%20the%20Deaf%20in%20Darjeeling%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Rupmani%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20a%20security%20guard%2C%20spent%20whatever%20he%20could%20to%20put%20her%20in%20a%20regular%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEfforts%20to%20express%20myself%20through%20sign%20language%20were%20met%20with%20punishment%20from%20teachers%20who%20failed%20to%20recognise%20my%20disability.%20Since%20I%20was%20a%20Deaf%20child%2C%20I%20felt%20isolated%20and%20unheard.%20My%20early%20education%20was%20mostly%20just%20copying%20notes%20without%20understanding%20concepts%2C%20except%20for%20geography%2C%20which%20I%20found%20more%20accessible%20due%20to%20its%20visual%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20extended%20family%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20would%20never%20succeed%20academically%20and%20saw%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20me%20as%20a%20futile%20effort.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20was%209%20or%2010%2C%20I%20had%20to%20start%20working%20to%20cover%20the%20costs%20of%20my%20school%20essentials.%20Making%20matters%20worse%2C%20I%20was%20also%20forced%20into%20speech%20therapy%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20available%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Helping%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communicate-with-kids-1727526887-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367955%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20Rupmani%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20struggles%20early%20on%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20that%20years%20later%20she%20would%20go%20on%20to%20co-found%20a%20venture%20called%20SignAble%20Communications%2C%20which%20among%20other%20things%2C%20has%20developed%20an%20app%20that%20provides%20a%20video%20relay%20service%20that%20empowers%20the%20Deaf%20to%20communicate%20and%20express%20themselves%20without%20barriers.%20The%20app%20offers%20Deaf%20persons%20%E2%80%9Caccess%20to%20a%20live%20interpreter%20at%20their%20fingertips%2C%20anytime%20and%20anywhere%2C%20all%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20app%2C%20Deaf%20people%20can%20communicate%20with%20essential%20service%20providers%20like%20the%20police%20and%20doctors%2C%20while%20also%20allowing%20them%20to%20communicate%20with%20their%20family%20and%20work%20colleagues.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20the%20remarkable%20story%20of%20how%20she%20found%20herself%20and%20developed%20an%20app%20which%20is%20helping%20open%20up%20different%20worlds%20for%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20who%20cannot%20hear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiscovering%20her%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20up%20till%20Class%209%2C%20she%20got%20married%20to%20her%20Deaf%20partner%20and%20they%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20initially%20saw%20marriage%20as%20a%20way%20to%20address%20my%20challenges%20and%20start%20anew%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi.%20After%20facing%20numerous%20difficulties%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%20I%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20return%20home%20but%20my%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20approve%20and%20insisted%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20her%20divorce%20in%202011%20that%20Rupmani%20resumed%20her%20studies%20and%20went%20on%20to%20finish%20high%20school.%20She%20would%20go%20on%20to%20earn%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20sociology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Delhi%20ultimately%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20opportunity%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20Deaf%20individuals%20in%20my%20early%20twenties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20witnessed%20sign%20language%20being%20used%20among%20the%20Deaf%20community.%20I%20longed%20to%20join%20them%2C%20but%20they%20often%20excluded%20me%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20sign%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20she%20found%20resources%20developed%20by%20organisations%20like%20the%20Noida%20Deaf%20Society%20(NDS)%20and%20%E2%80%98The%20Way%20Deaf%E2%80%99%20to%20learn%20sign%20language%2C%20supplemented%20by%20various%20YouTube%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESign%20language%20is%20the%20native%20language%20of%20the%20Deaf%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20individuals%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20communicate%20authentically%2C%20just%20like%20anyone%20else.%20It%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%2C%20and%20access%20to%20it%20should%20be%20provided%20from%20a%20young%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssisting%20her%20during%20this%20time%20in%20Delhi%20were%20disability%20rights%20activists%20like%20Geeta%20Sharma%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20the%20Deaf%20(NAD)%20and%20the%20late%20Javed%20Abidi%20from%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Employment%20for%20Disabled%20People%20(NCPEDP)%20who%20she%20believes%20played%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpivotal%20role%20in%20helping%20me%20discover%20the%20true%20essence%20of%20knowledge%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Deaf%20community%20and%20other%20specially-abled%20communities%20and%20provided%20invaluable%20guidance%20that%20has%20empowered%20me%20to%20navigate%20the%20world%20with%20confidence.%20I%20am%20deeply%20grateful%20for%20their%20support%20during%20this%20crucial%20phase%20of%20my%20life%3B%20without%20their%20mentorship%2C%20I%20would%20have%20felt%20lost.%20Through%20their%20encouragement%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F101036%2Fdelhi-cafe-hearken-hearing-impaired-staff%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20learned%20sign%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forged%20meaningful%20friendships%2C%20and%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20to%20discover%20my%20own%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20stint%20with%20the%20NAD%2C%20she%20began%20working%20with%20HAQ%3A%20Centre%20for%20Child%20Rights%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20non-profit.%20Her%20nearly%20six-year%20stint%20at%20HAQ%20landed%20her%20an%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%20(UNDP)%20in%202017%20in%20Europe%20where%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20she%20discovered%20the%20transformative%20impact%20of%20Video%20Relay%20Service%20(VRS)%20for%20the%20Deaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20blog%20published%20on%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unv.org%2Fdiversity-mosaic-inspirations%2Frupmani-chhetri-personifying-nothing-impossible%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20UN%20Volunteers%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMotivated%20to%20bring%20a%20change%2C%20Rupmani%20started%20her%20UN%20Volunteer%20journey%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20establishing%20a%20cross-cultural%20dialogue%20and%20exchange%20of%20knowledge%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Communications%20Assistant%2C%20she%20%E2%80%9Csupported%20the%20internally%20displaced%20people%20of%20the%20war%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fi-decided-to-become-a-special-educator-and-to-help-disabled-people-communicate-in-sign-language%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econducted%20sign%20language%20courses%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20teenagers%20and%20adults%20with%20hearing%20impairment%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20did%20the%20same%20for%20UN%20colleagues%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Germany%20and%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20said%20in%20the%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FRupmani-Chhetri-Pic-1727526989-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367956%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERupmani%20Chhetri%2C%20co-founder%20of%20SignAble%20Communications.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20war%2C%20some%20people%20had%20acquired%20disabilities%20or%20become%20injured%2C%20including%20around%20300%20Deaf%20people%20who%20had%20become%20displaced.%20They%20were%20asking%20me%2C%20as%20a%20fellow%20Deaf%20person%2C%20for%20help.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20help%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%2C%20especially%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder.%20Deaf%20people%20wanted%20to%20tell%20me%20their%20stories%20and%20what%20they%20went%20through.%20By%20being%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20give%20them%20a%20message%20of%20love%20and%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20UN%20Volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20one-and-a-half-year%20stint%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Rupmani%20also%20took%20part%20in%20multiple%20initiatives%20with%20other%20UN%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(OHCHR)%2C%20United%20Nations%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(UNICEF)%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20Refugee%20Agency%20(UNHCR).%20It%20was%20a%20truly%20rewarding%20time%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20facing%20numerous%20discouragements%2C%20I%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20embrace%20life%20as%20a%20series%20of%20risks%2C%20willing%20to%20try%20anything%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20I%20moved%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20travelled%20across%20Europe%2C%20where%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20robust%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20especially%20the%20availability%20of%20technology%20like%20VRS.%20This%20exposure%20allowed%20me%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20never%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESignAble%20for%20the%20Deaf%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20time%20in%20Europe%2C%20Rupmani%20came%20back%20to%20India.%20While%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%20she%20encountered%20Tarun%20Sarwal%2C%20who%20also%20returned%20to%20India%20after%20spending%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20working%20with%20humanitarian%20organisations%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20first%20met%20Mr%20Tarun%20while%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20after%20returning%20from%20my%20work%20at%20the%20UN.%20A%20common%20friend%20introduced%20us%20online%2C%20and%20during%20our%20initial%20conversations%2C%20Tarun%20asked%20how%20I%20could%20contribute%20to%20supporting%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20After%20many%20discussions%20about%20potential%20projects%20and%20ideas%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20meet%20in%20person.%20Our%20first%20face-to-face%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%201%20January%2C%202019%2C%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20amidst%20the%20Deaf%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20his%20time%20working%20in%20Geneva%20with%20an%20international%20humanitarian%20organisation%20that%20Tarun%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20difference%20an%20interpreter%20could%20make%20in%20a%20Deaf%20person%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SignAble%20Communications%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FSignAble-Communications-Team-1727527431-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%